hello ldef its so nice to have you back where you belong 
youre looking swell ldef we can tell ldef 
your music this morning is courtesy of the ldef project who 
are obviously very happy the control center told the astronauts 
we enjoyed doing it and are equally happy brandenstein 
responded 
