panels that had aluminum foil over look like theyve almost 
exploded i mean theyre just peeled back like a sardine can 
brandenstein said 
the satellite the size of a small school bus was being pulled 
to earth by atmospheric drag if the astronauts had not retrieved 
it trackers estimated it would have plunged to a fiery death in 
the atmosphere about march 9 its experiments lost forever 
